# 5. Detailed Working Example

# PROFIBUS Example

## Scenario

PLC controlling:

* 2 drives
* 16 DI module
* 16 DO module

### Communication Cycle

```text
PLC -> Drive1 status request
Drive1 -> Status response

PLC -> Drive2 status request
Drive2 -> Response

PLC -> Read DI
DI -> Input states

PLC -> Write DO
DO -> Output acknowledgment
```

Entire sequence repeats cyclically.

---

# PROFINET Example

## Scenario

PLC + Servo drives + HMI + Remote I/O

### Parallel Ethernet Communication

```text
PLC <-> Servo (IRT)
PLC <-> IO (RT)
HMI <-> PLC (TCP/IP)
SCADA <-> PLC (TCP/IP)
```

All coexist on same network.

