# 31. PROFIBUS vs PROFINET Frame Comparison

| Feature      | PROFIBUS        | PROFINET             |
| ------------ | --------------- | -------------------- |
| Basis        | Serial telegram | Ethernet frame       |
| Addressing   | Logical station | MAC + IP             |
| Error check  | FCS checksum    | CRC32                |
| Real-time    | Polling         | Prioritized Ethernet |
| Timing       | Token-based     | Scheduled Ethernet   |
| Payload size | Smaller         | Larger               |
| Speed        | 12 Mbps         | 100 Mbps+            |

